.DT
wimpy
$MUDNAME$ player help
wimpy

.SH Name
.SI 5
wimpy - set wimpy mode on or off
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
wimpy <num>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
You can set the percentage of your hit points at which you run away.  If
you have set the number to zero (default) you are in brave mode and won't
run away even if you are almost dead (in fact even if you are dead).
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
verbose, follow, lose
.EP
